QuestData.Title: Silly Wikket, Slickies are for Hozen
QuestData.Description: You think hozen crazy, wikket? Wait til you see hozen with no slickies!$b$bNot enough slickies for hozen and wikkets.$b$bSnappers! Hozen hate them ookin' snappers. Wikkets can eat all the snappers!$b$b<Eekle Eekle points to the south.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 4 Snapper Steaks from the Murky Bank.
